# (wildcard_tls) — cert config for the *.webxdc.* wildcard labels that
# routes.caddy serves. Wildcard certs need the DNS-01 challenge, which needs a
# caddy build with your DNS provider plugin compiled in (see README.md).
# The keep-alive comment below ensures the snippet still parses when every tls
# line is commented out.
(wildcard_tls) {
	# uncomment your provider at bring-up; requires a caddy build with the plugin (see README.md)
